In 78d1426fabd7b5b6cdd28de508a1692fce291174 "Add BIP352 test vectors as unit tests"

No need to have two `CExtKey`s and swapping them, you can just derive a key into itself.

```suggestion
    CExtKey key;
    key.SetSeed(seed);
    for (auto index : path) {
        BOOST_CHECK(key.Derive(key, index));
    }
    return key.key;
```

